flowchart TD
    Start([New Window]) --> ChampCheck{Champion<br/>exists?}

    ChampCheck -- No --> Train1[Train on window]
    Train1 --> Install[Install as champion]
    Install --> Log1[Log metrics]
    Log1 --> Done([Done])

    ChampCheck -- Yes --> Drift[Run Evidently<br/>drift detection]
    Drift --> DriftCheck{Drift<br/>detected?}

    DriftCheck -- No --> EvalChamp[Evaluate champion<br/>on new data]
    EvalChamp --> Keep1[Champion carries forward]
    Keep1 --> Log2[Log metrics]
    Log2 --> Done

    DriftCheck -- Yes --> Train2[Train challenger<br/>on new window]
    Train2 --> EvalBoth[Evaluate both on<br/>shared eval set]
    EvalBoth --> Compare{Challenger F1 ≥<br/>Champion F1 + 1%?}

    Compare -- Yes --> Promote[Promote challenger<br/>to champion]
    Promote --> Log3[Log both metrics]
    Log3 --> Done

    Compare -- No --> Retain[Retain champion]
    Retain --> Log4[Log both metrics]
    Log4 --> Done

    style Start fill:#6366f1,color:#fff,stroke:none
    style Done fill:#6366f1,color:#fff,stroke:none
    style Promote fill:#22c55e,color:#fff,stroke:none
    style Retain fill:#f59e0b,color:#fff,stroke:none
    style Install fill:#22c55e,color:#fff,stroke:none
    style Keep1 fill:#64748b,color:#fff,stroke:none
